### BrowserContext.clearCookies

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/release-notes-js.md

Enhanced method to clear cookies from a browser context with optional filters. Supports clearing all cookies, cookies by name, or cookies by domain.

```APIDOC
## BrowserContext.clearCookies()

### Description
Clears cookies from the browser context with optional filtering capabilities. Can remove all cookies or filter by name and domain.

### Method
POST (operation)

### Endpoint
BrowserContext.clearCookies(options)

### Parameters
#### Request Body
- **name** (string) - Optional - Clear only cookies with this specific name
- **domain** (string) - Optional - Clear only cookies for this specific domain

### Request Examples
```js
// Clear all cookies
await context.clearCookies();

// Clear cookies with a particular name
await context.clearCookies({ name: 'session-id' });

// Clear cookies for a particular domain
await context.clearCookies({ domain: 'my-origin.com' });
```

### Response
- Returns a Promise that resolves when cookies are cleared
- No response body
```

