### Clear Cookies with Filters in Playwright

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/release-notes-python.md

Clears cookies from a browser context with optional filtering by name or domain. Supports clearing all cookies, cookies with a specific name, or cookies for a particular domain.

```python
# Clear all cookies.
context.clear_cookies()
# New: clear cookies with a particular name.
context.clear_cookies(name="session-id")
# New: clear cookies for a particular domain.
context.clear_cookies(domain="my-origin.com")
```

